        "content": "<p>I think you could have used an inductive if each constructor takes the appropriate type as a parameter. Maybe something like:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ReducedRow</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">R0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ReducedRow0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rn0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ReducedRown0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or written differently:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ReducedRow</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">R0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ReducedRow0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"